Information Provided about Persona:

The information included about the persona was based on observational research, hallway research and optimized task flow analysis.

Effect of Persona on Design

What new features or design changes came from the personas?

Create visual reminders of tasks to focus the user since the stores being audited are highly unorganized.

Confirmation Screens

Ability to edit data quickly

Use the most accessible font for users with corrected vision

